creator: TimeClock Plus, LLC
descriptionHtml:
TCP MobileKiosk is an additional feature to the TCP software and is intended only for users that are licensed for that functionality.



Why TCP MobileKiosk? Revolutionize efficiency with an offering that only has the boundaries you create. With our mobile application you will have a secure, mobile and modern multi-user device option that enables your employees to interact with TCP in a sleek and dynamic mobile package.



Employees can quickly perform any operation necessary.



Key Features for Employees:

Clock in and out, or change your job code, with just the click of a button.

Remove unnecessary hassle and confusion with dashboard widgets.

Input time-off requests and view your accruals.

View and approve all your hours to streamline the payroll process.

Use offline punching for access in more remote areas.

Check schedules with one click.

Check notifications and messages.



TCP MobileKiosk is part of a workforce management solution that is meant to make the day-to-day easier; everything an employee can do in the app is granted by managers. This helps you make your employees more efficient by ensuring they have the mobile tools they need to succeed in today’s dynamic working environment while you continue to manage their access and avoid confusion.



TCP MobileKiosk also allows you to deploy a modern and efficient solution to your workforce in any environment you choose. Use TCP MobileKiosk for locations where a physical clock is impractical or impossible to deploy and enjoy the benefits of a mobile offering. All your employees can use the same mobile device for a portable, multi-purpose device option.



Submit questions or concerns directly to TCP Support:





New to TCP MobileKiosk? Find resources designed for you at https://timeclockplus.force.com/TCPSupport/s/.
